<p>protest.193 Security forces met protestors in the streets and responded with disproportionate 
force, firing live ammunition into the crowds, including from helicopters, killing many.194 
Most of the protestors were unarmed.195 The security forces also raided the homes of 
presumed opposition supporters, beating and killing residents.196 
